sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant FastAPI
    participant GroqAPI
    participant FallbackEngine

    User->>Frontend: Type message in chatbot
    Frontend->>FastAPI: POST /chatbot/query with history[]
    FastAPI->>FastAPI: Build messages = system_prompt + history + query
    FastAPI->>GroqAPI: POST chat/completions (Llama 3.3 70B)
    alt Success
        GroqAPI-->>FastAPI: AI response text
        FastAPI-->>Frontend: response
    else API Error or Timeout
        GroqAPI-->>FastAPI: Error / Timeout
        FastAPI->>FallbackEngine: Route to local rule-based engine
        FallbackEngine-->>FastAPI: Fallback response
        FastAPI-->>Frontend: Fallback response
    end
    Frontend-->>User: Display AI response in chat
